nodes.name: hydrogen selenide:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Hydrogen selenide + 3 NADP+ + 3 H2O <=> Selenite + 3 NADPH + 5 H+

nodes.name: ATP:selenide, water phosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: ATP + Hydrogen selenide + H2O <=> AMP + Selenophosphoric acid + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: Selenomethionine:tRNAMet ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Selenomethionine + tRNA(Met) <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Selenomethionyl-tRNA(Met)

nodes.name: selenite:reduced acceptor oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Selenite + H2O + Acceptor <=> Selenate + Reduced acceptor

nodes.name: selenophosphate:O-phospho-L-seryl-tRNA(Sec) selenium transferase
nodes.rxn: O-Phosphoseryl-tRNA(Sec) + Selenophosphoric acid + H2O <=> L-Selenocysteinyl-tRNA(Sec) + 2 Orthophosphate

nodes.name: L-selenocysteine selenide-lyase (L-alanine-forming)
nodes.rxn: L-Selenocysteine + Reduced acceptor <=> Hydrogen selenide + L-Alanine + Acceptor

nodes.name: methaneselenol:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: 2 NADPH + 2 H+ + Methylselenic acid <=> 2 NADP+ + 2 H2O + Methaneselenol
